# arubacloud_cloudserver (Data Source)

Retrieves read-only information about an existing `arubacloud_cloudserver` resource. Use this data source to reference a CloudServer's metadata (ID, URI, network configuration) in other Terraform configurations without managing the CloudServer lifecycle.

